title: Andrew WK - Partial discography (2001-2010) [FLAC][AMM]
description:
Automagical here!

This collection has the following albums of our favorite partygoer Andrew W.K.:

  Andrew WK - I Get Wet (2001)
  Andrew WK - The Wolf (2003)
  Andrew WK - Close Calls With Brick Walls (2006)
  Andrew WK - 55 Cadillac (2009)
  Andrew WK - Mother of Mankind (2010)

but frankly is missing some titles, like "The Japan Covers" and "Gundam Rock" (which are expensive as shit) so I couldn't exactly call this a complete discography. Still, good enough, I figure.
